text: Miriana Conte (born 17 December 2000), is a Maltese singer. She represented Malta at the Eurovision Song Contest 2025 with the song "Serving", where she finished 17th in the final with 91 points. ==Biography== Miriana Conte was born on 17 December 2000 in Qormi, Malta. She is half Italian, her father is from Naples and works as a businessman. In 2023 she was diagnosed with ADHD. She identifies as queer. ==Discography== ===Singles=== Title Year Peak chart positions Album MLT Air. MLT Dom. Air.
